title: Gonzalo Vicente
text:
Gonzalo Germán Vicente Maillot aka Gonzalo Vicente (born 22 December 1979 in <a href="Uruguay">Uruguay</a>) is a <a href="Uruguay">Uruguay</a>an <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> player.
Vicente played for <a href="Real%20Valladolid">Real Valladolid</a> and <a href="C%C3%A1diz%20CF">Cádiz</a> in the Spanish <a href="Segunda%20Divisi%C3%B3n">Segunda División</a>.
